OL,3,CMetropolitan police officer admits to
OL,4,Cstealing money from dead man
OL,6,FA Metropolitan police officer who
OL,7,Fstole money from a man who died after
OL,8,Fhe collapsed in the street has pleaded
OL,9,Fguilty to misconduct in public office.
OL,11,FPc Craig Carter stole around #115 from
OL,12,FClaudio Gaetani in September 2022,
OL,13,Fafter being handed a wallet following
OL,14,Fa sudden death.
OL,16,FCarter, from Harlow Essex, appeared in
OL,17,Fa dark suit at Wood Green Court to
OL,18,Fplead guilty to the charge.
