OL,6,FJudge Daniel Fugallo said: "I have to
OL,7,Fmake absolutely clear that an
OL,8,Fimmediate custodial sentence seems the
OL,9,Flikely outcome in this case but that
OL,10,Fwill be a matter for the sentencing
OL,11,Fjudge."
OL,13,FThe judge ordered a pre-sentence
OL,14,Freport and granted Carter
OL,15,Funconditional bail ahead of his
OL,16,Fsentencing at the same court on
OL,17,FSeptember 13.
